{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "a fakka tas KUNGS:\nNo-eij eekſch ta Kehnina\nno Juhda Namma/ un\nunna tur scho Wahrdụ."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un fakki: Klauſi ta KUNG-\nA Wahrdụ/ tu Kehninsch no\nJuhda/ kas tu tehdị us Dahwi-\na Gohda-Krehflu/ Tu/ un tawi\nKalpi/ un tawi Laudis/ kaszaur\nchahm Wahrtim ee-cet."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta fakka tas KUNGS:\nNeffet Teetu un Taifnibu/ un\nsglahbeet to Aplaupitu no ta\nApbehdinataja Rohkas/ un ne\nolehfeet to Sweſchineeku/ Bah-\ninu/ nedś Atraitni/ ne darrajt\nWarras-Darbu/ un ne iſleijeet\nchaî Weetā nenoseedsign Affini."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo kad juig ſcho Leetụ dar-\nifeet/ tad ee-ees zaur tcha Nam-\nna Wahrtim Kehnini/ kas us\nDahwida Gohda-Krehflu teh-\nehs/ un brauks ar Ratteem\nan Sirgeem/ tik labbi wiꞥſch/\na winna Kalpi/ un winna Lau-\nis."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ja juig ſchoß Wahrd-\nus ne gribbat klaufiht/ tad ef-\nnu es pee ſew paſcha ſwehrejs/\nfakka tas KUNGS: Ra ſchim\nNamnam buhs par pohstu Wee-\nu tapt."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo ta fakka tas KUNGS\nno ta Namna ta Kehnina Juh-\nda: Gileada tu man eſti eekſch\nibbanus ta Galwa/ ja es tikai\newi ne var Tuſſneti Darrụ/ un\nohs Pilſtahtus bes Eedsihwo-\najeem."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo es eezelfschu pahr tewi"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pohstitajus/ ikkatru ar fatweem\nEerohtſcheein/ tee nozirtihs ta-\nwus iswehletus Zeedra-Kohkus/\nun mettihs tohs Ugguni."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad ees dauds Pagann\nſchim Pilſfahtam fezzen/ un faz-\nzihs weens uhs ohtrụ; Rapehz\n1\nzihs weens uhs ohtrụ; Rapehz\n1\nirr tas KUNGS ta darrijs\nKalpi/ un tawi Laudis/ kaszaur\nchahm Wahrtim ee-cet."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee fazzihs: Tadeht ka\ntee irr atstahjuſchi to Derribu ta\nKUNGA fawa Deewa/ un\npreekſch zitteein Deeweem klan-\nnijschees/ un teem kalpojſchi."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne raudajt pahr to No-\nmirrutchu/ un ne noscheblojeet\nwinnu/ raudajt raudadami pahr\nto/ kas aiseet/ jo tas ne atgree-\nsifees atpakkat/ ka tas fawn\nDsintas-Senmi warretu re-\ndieht."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta fakka tas KUNGS\nno Salluma/ ta Dehla Josijus/\nta Kehnina no Juhda/ kas fawa\nTehwa Josijus Weetā walda/\nkas no ſchahs Weetas irr ats-\nanhits/ wiꞥſch ne atgreeſifees\nwairs atpakkat."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tai Weetā/ kurp tee\nwinnu irr aiſwedduſchi/ wiꞥſch\nnomirs/ un ſcho Senmi wiꞥſch\nwairs ne redſehs."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Waj tam! kas fawn\nNamnim ar Metaimibu ustaifa/\nun fawnas augſtas Istabas ar\nmetaifnu Buhschanu/ kas tawn\nTuwaku leek welti strahdaht/ un\nne dohd winnam fawn Alan."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas dohma/ es ustaiff-\nschu ſew weenu kohti augstu"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
